
Solution / Workaround:

Step One: Launch XAMPP Control Panel

Step Two: Select "Config" > my.ini

Step Three: Scroll down between:

"[mysqld]"
...and...
"port= 3306"

Step Four: Between "[mysqld]" and "port= 3306," type skip-grant-tables

Step Five: Save and exit.

Step Six: Retry launching Apache and MySQL.
